metadata.name: Episode I
metadata.description:
Close your eyes and let the Dream wash over you. 
Take a cup filled with water. With every sip you take, you will refresh your soul and mind, feel this life giving energy. The wisdom of water is infinite, it reminds you to dive beneath the surface of your feelings and use intuition. It is pure magic and is full of spiritual significance and powerful symbolism. Listen to your inner voice. Go for it and see what happens.Â
